dfrey ;  others derive the first part from the Germanic word <i>gawia</i> ‘territory’, <i>walah</i> ‘stranger’, or <i>gisil</i> ‘pledge’. Medieval forms can be found to support all these theories, and it is possible that several names have fallen together, or that the name was subjected to reanalysis by folk etymology at an early date."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Geoffrey Pigot was born in 1182, in Melmerby, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 2 sons with Geoffrey Pigot II. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"1182–":"1182–Surnud","1180–Male":"1180–Surnud","1205–1235":"1205–1235","1207–Male":"1207–Surnud","1182–Female":"1182–Surnud","1205":"1205","1235":"1235","1182":"1182","1207":"1207","1180":"1180","Melmerby, Yorkshire, England":"Melmerby, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Melmerby, Cumberland, England":"Melmerby, Cumberland, England"},"fi":{"1182–":"1182–Kuollut","1180–Male":"1180–Kuollut","1205–1235":"1205–1235","1207–Male":"1207–Kuollut","1182–Female":"1182–Kuollut","1205":"1205","1235":"1235","1182":"1182","1207":"1207","1180":"1180","Melmerby, Yorkshire, England":"Melmerby, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Melmerby, Cumberland, England":"Melmerby, Cumberland, England"},"fr":{"1182–":"1182–Décédée","1180–Male":"1180–Décédé","1205–1235":"1205–1235","1207–Male":"1207–Décédé","1182–Female":"1182–Décédée","1205":"1205","1235":"1235","1182":"1182","1207":"1207","1180":"1180","Melmerby, Yorkshire, England":"Melmerby, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Melmerby, Cumberland, England":"Melmerby, Cumberland, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Geoffrey Pigot est née en 1182, à Melmerby, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 2 fils avec Geoffrey Pigot II. Elle est décédée dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1182–":"1182–Verstorben","1180–Male":"1180–Verstorben","1205–1235":"1205–1235","1207–Male":"1207–Verstorben","1182–Female":"1182–Verstorben","1205":"1205","1235":"1235","1182":"1182","1207":"1207","1180":"1180","Me